sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant Frontend
    participant MCP as MCP Server
    participant VDB as Vector DB
    participant LLM

    User->>Frontend: Ask question about podcast
    Frontend->>MCP: Send query via RAG tool
    MCP->>VDB: Semantic search for relevant chunks
    VDB-->>MCP: Return top-k similar chunks
    MCP->>MCP: Build context from chunks
    MCP->>LLM: Send query + context
    LLM-->>MCP: Generate response
    MCP-->>Frontend: Return response + sources
    Frontend-->>User: Display answer with citations
